{"tid":748202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特指標指出現在美股狀態似2000年。","createTime":"2018-07-19T04:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T08:32:15.000Z","uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"389cb0cd067a0911e10a293c97e885eb3e828455","tid":748202,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"美股-巴菲特指標<br />\n股神巴菲特於2001年12月時，在富士比雜誌的一篇專文中提到： 用股市總市值和GNP的比值，可作為判斷整體股市是否過高或是過低， 因此被泛稱為巴菲特指標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.macromicro.me/collections/34/us-stock-relative/406/us-buffet-index-gspc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macromicro.me%2Fcollections%2F34%2Fus-stock-relative%2F406%2Fus-buffet-index-gspc&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=697156cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.macromicro.me/collections/34/us-stock-relative/406/us-buffet-index-gspc</a>"},{"pid":"f8e2a7d65f36bebaa93538a5e70790acda23a540","tid":748202,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"即係點？"},{"pid":"c6509170e70380c668d487d904ebe4fd21444704","tid":748202,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"中國好似300幾%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee408e475e69b9dc3a2aba9f1d6fb9758c878e3","tid":748202,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"08 年 得 120 左右<br />\n之後個十年印左好多銀紙 可能低估左國民購買能力"},{"pid":"210c9d52760d96ca1bdebee94e035de40035d8ac","tid":748202,"uid":29540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"即係升定跌呀 講重點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad13de47afd5b02b27cdbf9ef5b29422517df171","tid":748202,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210c9d52760d96ca1bdebee94e035de40035d8ac","tid":748202,"uid":29540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"rep